{"tid":1597542,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭對話會 = 進階班黑警記者會","createTime":"2019-09-27T03:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T06:18:26.000Z","uid":39205,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d77dbb33135b3e87df309db1e48d7c874b42f3fb","tid":1597542,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"一方面分散注意力，一方面做比藍絲<span style=\"color: gold;\">甚至外國</span>睇佢係有聆聽市民嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\n講左一萬次，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n退一步咁講，<span style=\"color: gold;\">無雙普選乜都係假</span>，就算其他四個做哂我地都係等比人清算。<br />\n<br />\n與其討論佢講乜，不如諗下點煲大佢。<br />\n<br />\n1. 大量武裝戒備警員陪同市民發言<br />\n2. 市民發現其中一名發言人為警員偽裝<br />\n3. 無視場外表達訴求市民比場內被挑選市民更多<br />\n4. 承諾不用新屋嶺更顯示該處曾有事故<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLRnyj7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLRnyj7.jpg&h=1a319d83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XzMyEZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzMyEZ7.jpg&h=fa03fcd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQAWCMO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQAWCMO.jpg&h=0b45da79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWcFjZ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWcFjZ9.jpg&h=9581228a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"272dd6b3d733018bf280ae0da22bd578b32bf736","tid":1597542,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"我地都要打幾巴<br />\n<br />\n紐約時報狠狠的一巴掌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1597351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1597351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d130a064f9aebd661f3d63dbb50f53220ceedb7","tid":1597542,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:54:34.000Z","msg":"再推下行動！<br />\n<br />\n【2350】未來幾日民間自發集會或遊行的不反對通知書申請狀況如下：<br />\n<br />\n9月27日（星期五）<br />\n<br />\n【聲援及關注新屋嶺被捕者人權集會】<br />\n時地：1930 中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\nTG頻道：<a href=\"https://t.me/VictimC